@214 = ~Flame Dart (Evocation)
Level: 1
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: 10 meters
Duration: instant
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: 1/2

When the preacher of flames casts this spell, a fiery dart leaves from his hands and goes straight to the designated target. It deals, at the impact, 1D3 fire damage points and there is a 50% chance of exploding, burning the target for additional 1D4 damage points for every 2 levels of the caster (max 10D4). If the target makes a successful saving throw vs. spells it suffers only half of the damage caused by burning.~
