@215 = ~Scorcher~
@216 = ~Scorcher (Evocation)
Level: 1
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: 20 m
Duration: 2 rounds
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 0.5 by 0 jet.
Saving Throw: none

Upon casting this spell a jet of flame appears at the caster's fingertips and bursts out toward one target of the caster's choice. That target will be hit by this flame for 2-16 points of damage. There is no saving throw against this spell. Other creatures who cross the path of the flame jet will also take damage as long as they stand in the flame. The flame jet stays for some time and still inflicts 2-6 points of damage the following round before dying out.~
